# BurnoutAI — Android App Setup Guide

## What the Android app does

| Feature | How it works |
|---|---|
| **App Usage Tracking** | Reads which apps you used today using Android UsageStatsManager |
| **Study vs Entertainment** | Classifies apps (Google Classroom, Duolingo = Study / Instagram, YouTube = Entertainment) |
| **Step Counter** | Uses phone's built-in step counter sensor for physical activity data |
| **Sleep Estimation** | Asks you each day for sleep hours (slider in Check-In) |
| **Sends to Backend** | All data is sent via HTTP to the Python backend running on your PC |
| **Shows Results** | Live burnout score, risk factors, and recommendations on the phone |

